undi ani convince chestadu , mali nuvu dapu e movie no accurate ending . hero antadu money kosam avrino ama analenu and pechina ama aunty analenu . ending lo hero company co ipotadu but that is not he heroine to anduku matladatado clarity undadu my whole point is to disagree to point that is ala vaikuntapuram lo is great and is average . small budget cinema inta baga tisadu ani chepakunda arey peda
